PointName: San Francisco Museum of Modern Art
Description: The San Francisco Museum of Modern Art (SFMOMA) is a modern art museum located in San Francisco, California. A nonprofit organization, SFMOMA holds an internationally recognized collection of modern and contemporary art and was the first museum on the West Coast devoted solely to 20th century art. The museumﾒs current collection includes over 29,000 works of painting, sculpture, photography, architecture, design, and media arts.
